{
  "title": "Vi vim 显示行号 色彩",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 26pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">linux vi vim&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 26pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">显示行号 色彩</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">今天下午在<span lang=\"EN-US\">Linux</span>上编写<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>感觉没有色彩真的很悲剧。于是乎网上狂搜，解决方法很多人都提到了，可是设置完了不好使。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">下面说一下我自己的误区：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">主要原因是忘记将<span lang=\"EN-US\">vi</span>设置为<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>的别名了。此处需要安装<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>下面会提到。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">alias vi=vim<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">解决方法也顺便列出来：找到根目录下的<span lang=\"EN-US\">etc</span>文件夹。<span lang=\"EN-US\">locate vimrc</span>找<span lang=\"EN-US\">vimrc</span>的位置<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">cd etc<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">vi vimrc<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">在<span lang=\"EN-US\">vimrc</span>的最后添加：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">set nu</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">&nbsp;//</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">显示行号<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">set ts=4//tab</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">占<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>个字符<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">set autoindent</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">set cindent<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">syntax enable</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">其中<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;autoindent&nbsp;</span>是自动缩进；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;cindent</span>是特别针对<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;C</span>语言语法自动缩进<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">网上其他解决方案：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3'; color: rgb(251, 0, 7);\">vi</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3'; color: rgb(251, 0, 7);\">是没有颜色的，<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>是有颜色的。可是系统中没有安装<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3'; color: rgb(251, 0, 7);\">我们可以通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;rpm -qa |grep vim&nbsp;</span>看看系统中是否安装了下面<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>个<span lang=\"EN-US\">rpm</span>包，如果有就是安装了<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">[root@203 ~]# rpm -qa |grep vimvim-minimal-7.0.109-3vim-enhanced-7.0.109-3vim-common-7.0.109-3<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">如果没有则下载着<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>个包，然后安装<span lang=\"EN-US\">[root@203 ~]# rpm -ivh vim-common-7.0.109-3.x86_64.rpm[root@203 ~]# rpm -ivh vim-enhanced-7.0.109-3.x86_64.rpm</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">[root@203 ~]# rpm -ivh vim-minimal-7.0.109-3<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">然后<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>命令可用，且有颜色，但是<span lang=\"EN-US\">vi</span>还是没有颜色，我们需要修改<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;~/.bashrc</span>文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">[root@203 ~]# vi ~/.bashrc</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">加入<span lang=\"EN-US\">alias vi='vim'</span>这样<span lang=\"EN-US\">vi</span>就有颜色了，如果感觉颜色暗淡，那我们进入下一步<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">进入<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">color</span>目录（<span lang=\"EN-US\">/usr/share/vim70/colors,</span>不同的系统目录不同，建议在～<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>建立<span lang=\"EN-US\">.vim</span>目录，然后在些目录里建立对应的文件夹和文件）<span lang=\"EN-US\">$ ls /usr/share/vim/vim70/colorsblue.vim</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">delek.vim</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">&nbsp;evening.vim murphy.vim</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">&nbsp;README.txt torte.vimdarkblue.vim desert.vim</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">koehler.vim pablo.vim</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">&nbsp;ron.vim</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">&nbsp;zellner.vimdefault.vim</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">&nbsp;elflord.vim morning.vim peachpuff.vim shine.vim</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">然后再自己的<span lang=\"EN-US\">~HOME/</span>建立一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;.vimrc</span>文档</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">[$ vi .vimrc:colorscheme evening</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Verdana;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB W3';\">，假如选择其他的方案 只要替换<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;evening&nbsp;</span>就能够了！然后再打开<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim&nbsp;</span>看一下是不是颜色变得好看了！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><span title=\"neteasefooter\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><span id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 10px 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px;\">来自网易手机号码邮箱<a id=\"mobile_set\" sys=\"1\" log=\"1\" logid=\"free_sms_20120504\" href=\"http://shouji.163.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">了解更多</a></div></div></span></span>"
    }
  ]
